    <section id="id1166412529870">
      <title>ARS†42-17257 Notice of Change in District Boundaries </title>
      <para id="id1166402046198">On or before November 1 of the year preceding the year in which assessments or taxes are to be levied, does the Governing Board file with the Department of Revenue and the appropriate county assessor, information prescribed by the director of the department as to any change in boundaries of the district?
      </para>
      
      
      <para id="id1166429986936">[ ] Yes   [ ] No</para>
    </section>
    <section id="id1166417243210">
      <title>ARS†42-11104 Exemption for education property</title>
      <para id="id1166405644242">Does the district recognize that “libraries, school buildings and other buildings used for education with their furniture, equipment and land are exempt from taxation, including property and equipment pursuant to a lease or lease purchase agreement?
      </para>
      
      
      <para id="id1166404627443">[ ] Yes   [ ] No</para>
    </section>
    <section id="id1166414620986">
      <title>ARS Title 43</title>
      <para id="para-id1166414620986">
